# Business Domain

Read authoritative docs **before** changing CRUD, seasons, stats, or dashboard metrics.

## Functional rules

`docs/informacao/dominio/regras-de-negocio.md`

Key themes (details in doc):

- Players: soft delete; required name/position
- Championships: at most one active season; finalize → titles
- Matches: stats consistency on CRUD; embedded player stats
- Teams: cannot delete with active players

## Metrics and KPIs

**Source of truth:** `docs/informacao/analytics/metrics-catalog.md`

Do not redefine metric semantics in code comments or handlers — align with catalog or update catalog first.

## Analytics jobs

In-process thread pool — `src/galaticos/analytics/player_stats_jobs.clj`

Not Redis/Sidekiq. Job status via `player_stats_job_store`.

## Player merge

Follow `src/galaticos/handlers/player_merge.clj` and merge audit collections in `db/merge_audit.clj`, `db/player_merge_refs.clj`.

## Reconciliation

Operational analytics issues: `docs/informacao/analytics/reconciliation-runbook.md`
